Note: because the pharmacy information will be entered into the pharmacy form, None = No ART during labor is not an option. The women will simply not have a pharmacy form filled in. Tail will be captured as part of the post natal pharmacy form. A quesiton to be explored is how many pharmacy forms would be filled in. If all of the medications given during the maternity stay are on one form, we need to change the form to show the LAST ARV regimen dispensed. This information is required for the Track 1.0 report. We also need to understand how the counting works for a woman who delivers the last day of the month - and is still receiving medication into the next month.
